<h3>Send us your old hardware</h3>

<p>We want Sukey to work perfectly on every device in existence. However, all the Sukey devs are nerds so use Android devices and shun Apple. We need old iPhones, iPads, Nokias, BlackBerrys and literally anything else that can support an app or access the internet! If you've got any you'd like to give or lend, please <a href="/contact">drop us a note</a>.</p>

<h3>Give your time</h3>

<p>If you have skills that coul help Sukey and the time to get involved please let us know. Maybe you're a programmer, a security expert, somebody who will help us to test new releases, or maybe you're pretty good at making sandwiches and ordering pizzas.  If you have time to spare and share our passion for what we're doing then <a href="/contact">please get in touch</a>.</p>
